{"tid":810693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"齊齊加入工聯會盡享福利","createTime":"2018-09-08T07:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T16:16:54.000Z","uid":182114,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e53b2dcdc6c3e174bc0c99635a19cedab80194f2","tid":810693,"uid":182114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"港區人大鄭耀棠建議香港在惠州、中山等地，租地建<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「港式新市鎮」</span></strong>，可以住50至60萬人，香港擁有土地的管理權或高度自治權，行香港法律。而原先在當地居住的居民，除了提供搬遷補償，亦可考慮讓他們在新市鎮住滿7年，就取得香港永久居民身分。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時見到呢d新聞都火撚滾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之但係.. 我見工聯會成日好多福利...<br />\n<br />\n因為....中共旗下香港工聯會的財務，向來秘而不宣，但其最近一份財務報告副本為《蘋果日報》所得，披露工聯會過去三年獲<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">二億四千萬元捐款</span></strong>......xxxxxx。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而吳秋北答「工會的財務安排有其必要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">性需要</span></strong>，合情合理。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ne.g. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">九龍社團辦中秋茶聚 $38 食 12 餸</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗宜傢參加定,宜傢咪話係個會買乜買物有得平ge,用左先,<br />\n到第時老左又有得食到盡 (只要食唔死人的話)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E5%80%A1%E5%90%91%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%A7%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%8C%E6%B8%AF%E5%BC%8F%E6%96%B0%E5%B8%82%E9%8E%AE%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E9%84%AD%E8%80%80%E6%A3%A0%EF%BC%9A%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E4%BD%8F%E6%BB%BF7%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%AF%E7%8D%B2%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89%E3%80%80-6GrNXX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E5%2580%25A1%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%25A7%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2