%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2587%25B1%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD-kLeDgo&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fx2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ef253270\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E7%A4%BE%E5%9C%98%E8%BE%A6%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%8B%E8%8C%B6%E8%81%9A+38+%E9%A3%9F+12+%E9%A4%B8%E3%80%80%E4%B8%BB%E8%BE%A6%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%9A%E9%99%B3%E5%87%B1%E6%AC%A3%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD-kLeDgo</a>"},{"pid":"3568bbf348ebb7efa56c33c6ee1d0b8cdb650063","tid":810693,"uid":182114,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"想問下做工會會員邊個行業最平會費"},{"pid":"2e9e052bf9bba9dc7c7c9d46859fee5f7086ea10","tid":810693,"uid":182114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb1e6663602ced3da8adff538ffc9c7b47b4a3a","tid":810693,"uid":182114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"大家連食窮佢ge心態都唔肯???"},{"pid":"56f04fe29f8ba7748af696f9ea2b1098ff02b43c","tid":810693,"uid":182114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>吳秋北轟法官社會罪人　專業議政譴責：對法律法治無知　促請政府回應</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反新界東北發展十三子上周獲終審法院判上訴得直，當庭釋放，工聯會會長吳秋北在Facebook發文狠批法官「縱惡」，害死青年，為社會埋下定時炸彈，「法官老爺已為青年殺手，社會罪人！」專業議政發聲明嚴厲譴責吳秋北，批評他對法律和法治原則無知，更對法官作人身攻擊，要求他收回言論，及向法官及公眾道歉。<br />\n<br />\n專業議政在聲明指，終審法院院不是裁決新界東北案13名示威者無罪，而是參照2014年衝擊立法會案上訴庭的量刑，而反東北威的案情相對較輕，但上訴庭對該案示威者的量刑起點，大幅提高至15個月，因此終院判示威者上訴得直。終院法官只是按照現行法律及過往案例判案。<br />\n<br />\n專業議政批評，吳秋北的言論，顯示他妄顧案件事實，對法律和法治無知，更對法官人身攻擊，要嚴厲譴責吳秋北，並要求他收回言論，向法官及公眾道歉。專業議政亦促請政府回應吳秋北的言論，以維護法治及尊重司法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E5%90%B3%E7%A7%8B%E5%8C%97%E8%BD%9F%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%BD%AA%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%80%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%94%BF%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%8D%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E7%84%A1%E7%9F%A5%E3%80%80%E4%BF%83%E8%AB%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-x1MBz1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25BD%259F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259F%25A5%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25BF%2583%25E8%25AB%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589-x1MBz1&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fx2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=34ee569d\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E5%90%B3%E7%A7%8B%E5%8C%97%E8%BD%9F%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%BD%AA%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%80%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%94%BF%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%8D%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E7%84%A1%E7%9F%A5%E3%80%80%E4%BF%83%E8%AB%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-x1MBz1</a>"},{"pid":"d15d1ab4e74f9637dfd6d3d48a6f6eb8bb4be160","tid":810693,"uid":182114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc186428c91be5acb44ac21cac15e46d75eb4e7","tid":810693,"uid":182114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T17:47:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkftustsc.org/info/m1001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkftustsc.org%2Finfo%2Fm1001.html&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fx2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5219c961\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkftustsc.org/info/m1001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkftustsc.org/images/calendar18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkftustsc.org%2Fimages%2Fcalendar18.jpg&h=6d5b24d6